with customers as (

    select * from ANALYTICS.DBT_ANAMISI.stg_jaffle_shop__customers

),

orders as (
    
    select * from ANALYTICS.DBT_ANAMISI.stg_jaffle_shop__orders    

),

customer_orders as (

    select
        customer_id,

        min(order_date) as first_order_date,
        max(order_date) as most_recent_order_date,
        count(order_id) as number_of_orders

    from orders

    group by 1

),

-- Computes total spent by each customer
customer_total_spent as (

    select
        customer_id,
        sum(amount) as lifetime_value
    from ANALYTICS.DBT_ANAMISI.fct_orders
    group by 1
),

final as (

    select
        customers.customer_id,
        customers.first_name,
        customers.last_name,
        customer_orders.first_order_date,
        customer_orders.most_recent_order_date,
        coalesce(customer_orders.number_of_orders, 0) as number_of_orders,
        customer_total_spent.lifetime_value

    from customers

    left join customer_orders using (customer_id)
    left join customer_total_spent using (customer_id)

)

select * from final
